import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { HeaderService } from 'src/app/Services/header.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-header', templateUrl: './header.component.html', styleUrls: ['./header.component.scss'] }) export class HeaderComponent { selectedOption: string | null = null; constructor( private router :Router, private headerService:HeaderService ){ this.selectedOption = "admin" } navigateToLoginAdmin(){ this.headerService.userIs("admin") this.selectedOption="admin" this.router.navigate(['/login']); } navigateToLoginStudent(){ this.selectedOption="student" this.headerService.userIs("student") this.router.navigate(['/login']); } navigateToLoginCompany(){ this.selectedOption="company" this.headerService.userIs("company") this.router.navigate(['/login']); } }
